          <input type="date" name="dob" placeholder="1 january 2025" required>
          <p>school*</p>
          <input type="text" name="school" placeholder="the cool school" required>
          <p>how did you find keepsake?</p>
          <input type="text" name="source" placeholder="instagram / slack / XX told me..." value="">

